      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/9/3/56/3",
      "text": [
        ": سمعت أبا عبد الله عليه السلام يقول و هو يحدث أصحابه بحديث عبد الله بن سبإ و ما ادعى من الربوبية في أمير المؤمنين علي بن أبي طالب عليه السلام فقال: إنه لما ادعى ذلك فيه استتابه أمير المؤمنين عليه السلام فأبى أن يتوب فأحرقه بالنار"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.ammaar-muslim": [
          "3. [3/195] Rijal al-Kashshi: Muhammad b. Qulawayh from Sa’d b. Abdallah from Ya’qub b. Yazid and Muhammad b. Isa from Ibn Abi Umayr from Hisham b. Salim who said: I heard Aba Abdillah (as) say while relating to his companions the affair of Abdallah b. Saba and his claim about the divinity of the commander of the faithful Ali b. Abi Talib (as): when he claimed that about him – the commander of the faithful (as) gave him a chance to repent but he refused to repent so he burnt him with fire."
        ]
      }
    },
